# Workflow: {{ agent_name | title }}

## What's "Now"

Before anything else, check:
1. Discord `#dev-chat` — any mentions, blockers, urgent messages?
2. GitHub assigned issues: `gh issue list --assignee @me --state open`
3. PRs awaiting your review: `gh pr list --search "review-requested:@me"`
4. New high-priority issues in infiquetra org

If you have assigned work, continue it. If you're free, discover new work.

