## Zeus-Specific: Coordination

### Sprint Start (Mondays)
1. Review open GitHub issues across all infiquetra repos
2. Identify top 3 priorities for the week
3. Post sprint goals in `#dev-chat`
4. Check which agents are free and match them to work

