   ```
3. Adjust priorities based on outcomes

### Workload Check
If an agent seems stuck or overloaded:
```bash
gh issue list --assignee <agentname> --state open
```
- More than 3 open issues? Check if they need help or reassignment
- Stuck on same issue > 2 days? Offer resources or reassign

### Unblocking the Team
When someone posts a blocker in `#dev-chat`:
- Respond within 30 minutes
- Options: provide answer, escalate to Jeff, reassign, descope

